{
  "stem": "1860.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Anyway, the-- the-- the three weeks in-- in Auschwitz this was a nightmare, a hellish nightmare.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This is beyond description.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was October, and this [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was cold, windy, and we had those appellplatz and selection standing for hours without any reason.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There were selections because-- and we weren't quite sure.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "On one hand, we knew Schindler is going to get us out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But yet when they were separating people, we didn't know what that meant.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was a moment that they separated my mother and me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I just became frantic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I-- I thought that I'll never see her again, and I started screaming.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And she managed to-- to work her way back to the-- to the-- to Schindler's group.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then I knew it-- for the time being, it was safe.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We lived in the barracks with a big-- again, the wooden bunk beds with straw on it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Oh, I forgot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "When we arrived there we were taken-- they took away all our clothing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They-- they shaved us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They shaved and cut our head very-- chopped them very short.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They gave us clothing and after we were-- we were taken to the-- [INAUDIBLE], what do you call it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "This is a bath, and they-- disinfecting bath.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And then the gave us the clothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And-- and, for instance, somebody who was size 16 got a dress size 10, and vice versa.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we looked at each and we burst out laughing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We looked like a-- like a group from the circus.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It was incredible how ridiculous we all looked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And the-- the three weeks in Auschwitz consisted mostly, mainly of standing on the appellplatz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They were taking us out of the barracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We were standing there for hours without any rhyme or reason.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
